                    <h2>Overview</h2>
                    <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. — Formerly known as thyssenkrupp Industries India Pvt. Ltd.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="comp-body">
                    <p>TKIL Industries is a prominent name in the engineering sector, specializing in the design, manufacture, supply, construction, and maintenance of industrial plants and systems. Since its inception in 1947, TKIL Industries has been at the forefront of delivering cutting-edge solutions in capital goods, spanning across mining, material handling, mineral processing, cement, energy, green hydrogen, boilers, bio-chemicals, battery &amp; energy storage, sugar and cogen industries, contributing significantly to India's industrial growth.</p>
                    <p>TKIL Industries, we remain dedicated to innovation, efficiency, and sustainability. We continue to drive progress in industries that are vital to both economic growth and environmental preservation. Our focus on superior product quality, adherence to international standards, timely project delivery, hassle-free operation, low maintenance, and prompt technical support ensures that we meet the highest expectations of our clients.</p>
                </div>
